  i  am  objecting  to  the  introduction  of  the  interstate  river  water disputes  amendment  bill  2017  do  this  parliament  and  the  government  have the power to have a law in this manner  i am not going into the merit of the bill  at this juncture i am only saying that this is very wrongly drafted bill  my only request  to  the  government  is  to  reconsider  introduction  of  this  bill    the government may prepare a good draft after consulting the respective provinces and come back to this house  